{"componentChunkName":"component---src-layouts-blog-post-layout-js","path":"/blog/dawn-theme-clickable-banner-tutorial","result":{"pageContext":{"id":1339,"date":"2022-01-13T10:36:10","date_gmt":"2022-01-13T10:36:10","guid":{"rendered":"https://www.ezfy.club/?p=1339"},"modified":"2022-02-16T14:17:22","modified_gmt":"2022-02-16T14:17:22","slug":"dawn-theme-clickable-banner-tutorial","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https://www.ezfy.club/dawn-theme-clickable-banner-tutorial/","title":{"rendered":"Dawn theme: how to make the image banner clickable"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Are you trying to make your Dawn theme&#8217;s banner section image clickable? Look no further! Although the Dawn&#8217;s banner section comes with buttons that you can add links to, there is no way to make the image itself clickable. Well, up until now! <br><br>With this guide I&#8217;ll teach you how you can make your banner clickable just by pasting some code into your theme.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-making-a-backup-of-your-current-theme\">Making a backup of your current theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Before diving into the tutorial make sure you download the theme, so in case you face any issues you can easily revert back.<br><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1514\" height=\"481\" class=\"wp-image-503\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123.png 1514w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-600x191.png 600w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-1200x381.png 1200w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/dl-123-768x244.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1514px) 100vw, 1514px\" /></p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-adding-the-code-to-your-theme\">Adding the code to your theme</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From your Shopify Admin go to: <strong>online store &gt; themes &gt; actions &gt; edit code</strong></li><li>Find the file named exactly <strong>&#8220;image-banner.liquid&#8221;</strong><br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"789\" height=\"498\" class=\"wp-image-1429\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/x11.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/x11.jpg 789w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/x11-768x485.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 789px) 100vw, 789px\" /></li><li>Delete everything in there and paste this code:<br><br>[gist]c44eb67f982fcbfdeaa48dd0b0e67920[gist]<br></li><li>Now click on the &#8220;save&#8221; button on the top right.</li></ol>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"h-adding-a-link-to-your-image-banner\">Adding a link to your image banner</h3>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>From the &#8220;Customize&#8221; page, click on the &#8220;Image Banner&#8221; section.<br><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"884\" height=\"346\" class=\"wp-image-1345\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/imagem_2022-01-13_071652.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/imagem_2022-01-13_071652.png 884w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/imagem_2022-01-13_071652-850x333.png 850w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/imagem_2022-01-13_071652-768x301.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 884px) 100vw, 884px\" /></li><li>You&#8217;ll see a new option at the top named &#8220;Link&#8221;:<br> <img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"795\" height=\"291\" class=\"wp-image-1347\" style=\"width: 600px;\" src=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/imagem_2022-01-13_071748.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/imagem_2022-01-13_071748.png 795w, https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/imagem_2022-01-13_071748-768x281.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 795px) 100vw, 795px\" /></li><li>Simply add the link you want and you&#8217;re all set! </li></ol>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also choose to open it in a new tab if you wish. Keep in mind that, if you have added any buttons, this new link will overwrite their URLs.</p>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"you-may-also-like\">You may also like</h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Here are some other tutorials you may be interested in:<br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/dawn-theme-product-page-slideshow-with-arrows-tutorial\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Arrows &amp; vertical thumbnails for Dawn&#8217;s product pages<span><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media3.giphy.com/media/w4LaQF8cp1akInO4Cp/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/dawn-theme-how-to-fix-zoom-images-size-mobile-desktop?source=blog-dawn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Dawn lightbox: responsive images, slider and arrows <span><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://media4.giphy.com/media/aBmvXTlfvHiPMXtx4a/giphy.gif\"></span></a><br><a href=\"https://ezfycode.com/blog/how-to-disable-right-click-image-and-text-copying-without-apps?source=blog-dawn\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">&#8211; Improve your website&#8217;s safety: block right click, image copying and more</a></p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Learn how to make the original Dawn theme&#8217;s banner clickable without heavy customizations.</p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":1351,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[9],"tags":[435],"image_alt":"","acf":[],"featured_image_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/debut_slideshow-5-850x478.png","featured_image_small_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/debut_slideshow-5-200x200.png","featured_image_large_src":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/debut_slideshow-5-1200x675.png","post_count":null,"categories_names":["Blog"],"tag_names":["Dawn Theme"],"featured_image_url":"https://www.ezfy.club/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/debut_slideshow-5.png","featured_image_url_alt":"","_links":{"self":[{"href":"https://www.ezf